    "description": "<h3><a name=\"Summary\"></a>Summary</h3>\n\n<p>Prepare test data and validate environment readiness for execution.</p>\n\n<h3><a name=\"Context\"></a>Context</h3>\n\n<p>This issue involves verifying the accessibility of specific web pages and ensuring that test data is ready for execution. It also includes validating selectors against the live DOM.</p>\n\n<h3><a name=\"Acceptancecriteria\"></a>Acceptance criteria</h3>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>Verify accessibility of:\n\t<ul>\n\t\t<li><a href=\"https://demoqa.com/text-box\" title=\"smart-link\" class=\"external-link\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">https://demoqa.com/text-box</a></li>\n\t\t<li><a href=\"https://demoqa.com/webtables\" title=\"smart-link\" class=\"external-link\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">https://demoqa.com/webtables</a></li>\n\t\t<li><a href=\"https://demoqa.com/radio-button\" title=\"smart-link\" class=\"external-link\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">https://demoqa.com/radio-button</a></li>\n\t</ul>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>Extract negative test data from Validation Matrix (Excel).</li>\n\t<li>Validate selectors against live DOM:\n\t<ul>\n\t\t<li><tt>#userEmail</tt></li>\n\t\t<li><tt>#age</tt>, <tt>#salary</tt></li>\n\t\t<li><tt>#noRadio</tt></li>\n\t</ul>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>Ensure selector references are up-to-date and stable.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n<h3><a name=\"Otherinformation\"></a>Other information</h3>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>All target pages should be accessible.</li>\n\t<li>Test data must be prepared and ready for execution.</li>\n\t<li>Selectors need to be verified and usable for automation.</li>\n</ul>\n",
